.impersonation-start.well.p-3.my-3.rounded-3
  %header.admin-actions__head
    %span.admin-actions__title
      %i.fa-solid.fa-user-secret{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      Impersonation
    %span.admin-actions__subtitle
      %i.fa-solid.fa-lock{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      Admin-only

  %p.impersonation-start__lede
    Operate as another user. <strong>Act as</strong> attributes any deposits or edits wholly to that user, with your own identity recorded in the audit trail; <strong>View as</strong> is read-only and shows exactly what they can see. A persistent banner marks the session, which ends on an attempted write during View-as (the write is blocked) or after 30 minutes idle.

  = form_tag admin_act_as_path, method: :post, class: 'impersonation-start__form' do
    .impersonation-start__field
      = label_tag :nuid, 'Target NUID', class: 'impersonation-start__label'
      = text_field_tag :nuid, nil, class: 'form-control impersonation-start__input', placeholder: 'e.g. 000000002', autocomplete: 'off', inputmode: 'numeric'
    .impersonation-start__actions
      = submit_tag 'Act as', name: 'mode', class: 'btn btn-danger', formaction: admin_act_as_path
      = submit_tag 'View as', name: 'mode', class: 'btn btn-warning', formaction: admin_view_as_path
